title: War of the Roses: The Honeymoon Phase Died So Fast
description: Zoey has been with her boyfriend for 6 months and they used to be hooking up ALL the time as a lot of couples do at the beginning of the relationship, but recently her boyfriend isn't trying to hook up at all.  Why such a flip of the switch?  Is he getting it elsewhere?
